# 🔹 Why Graph Algorithms?

Many real-world problems are modeled as graphs:

* 🌐 Computer Networks
* 🗺️ GPS Navigation
* 📱 Social Networks
* ✈️ Airline Route Planning
* 🤖 AI Path Finding

Graph algorithms help solve:

* Traversal
* Shortest Path
* Cycle Detection
* Dependency Resolution
* Network Optimization

